BT 1 0 0 1 0 51 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (2. ) Tj /F2 9 Tf (Earth's magnetosphere is a planetary-scale Debye shield.) Tj /F1 9 Tf ( The same formula that governs the biological Debye layer) Tj T* (\(lambda_D = sqrt\(epsilonkT/2n_0q^2\)\) applies to the magnetosphere at planetary scale. During geomagnetic storms, the) Tj T* (magnetosphere's shielding efficiency decreases -- equivalent to a biological organism having its Debye layer suddenly) Tj T* (thinned. The ELF/VLF noise increase during the storm's main phase \(0.001-100 Hz band\) directly overlaps cardiac) Tj T* (pacemaker frequency \(1 Hz\) and neural oscillations, adding DELTAgamma to any biological system near its gamma_c.) Tj T* ET
